metadata.name: SUSI BAKA #01
metadata.description:
Art by Mirasolitude  
https://twitter.com/Mirasolitude

Given as a gift to all bidders in the auction for ANGEL #03 - RAZIEL (from the Aswang Collection) on 22 March 2023.

This item can be burned together with Susi Baka #02 & Susi Baka #03 to claim Susi Baka #04.

Editions: 10 of 10
